- `kernel/build.rs` packs every server in `servers` array into the archive
- `boot_image/mod.rs` embeds the archive via `include_bytes!(env!("BOOT_IMAGE_PATH"))`
- `userland::userland_bootstrap` iterates and loads all servers
- **Adding RS**: just add to `build.rs` `servers` array; the archive will include it and it loads automatically

